client (game)
get  -> server:     create room, res back roomID and app
res  -> client(g):  display lobby, wait for players (and game start signal)

client (player)
get  -> server:     instantiate player object, res entrance form
res  -> client(p):  display entrance form (enter roomID and name)
emit -> server:     assign player's name and add to correct room, send lobby init signal, then wait for start
res  -> client(p):  display lobby. game host has a start button, sends start signal
emit -> server:     recieves start signal, begins game

server
emit -> client(g): start the game